== Related articles == * {{ill|Kayanarumi|ja|カヤナルミ}} - A deity appearing in the ''{{ill|Engishiki|ja|延喜式}}'' (巻八, ''Izumo Province Norito''), thought to have a connection due to the shared element "Narumi." * {{ill|Nunobutomi-Torinarumi-no-Kami|ja|布忍富鳥鳴海神}} - The thirteenth generation deity among the Seventeen Generations of Gods.
