'''Torinarumi-no-Kami''' (鳥鳴海神, トリナルミ, {{lang-en|Torinarumi-no-Kami|qq=draft|qq=draft}}) is a {{ill|Japanese mythology|ja|日本神話|deity in Japanese mythology=deity in Japanese mythology|lt=deity in Japanese mythology|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese mythology|qq=}}.
== Overview == Torinarumi-no-Kami is a deity mentioned in the {{ill|Kojiki|ja|古事記|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kojiki|qq=}} and belongs to the {{ill|17 spirits of the world|simple|user:immanuelle/17 spirits of the world|ja|十七世神|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/17 spirits of the world|qq=}} (とおまりななよのかみ). This deity is classified as a {{ill|Kunitsukami|ja|国津神|1=Kunitsukami|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kunitsukami|13=User:Immanuelle/Kunitsukami|qq=}} and is only described by name in the text. The name is interpreted as "a bird that carries spirits, resonating through the sea"{{Sfn|Nishimiya|2014|p=381}}.
== Genealogy == [[File:Ohokuninushi family tree.png|right|thumb|250px|Genealogy of Ōkuninushi (according to the ''Kojiki''). Blue represents male deities, red female deities, and yellow indicates unknown gender.]] Torinarumi-no-Kami was born from the union of {{ill|Ōkuninushi|ja|大国主神|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ōkuninushi|qq=}} and his wife, {{ill|Tottori-no-Kami|ja|鳥取神|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tottori-no-Kami|qq=}}, the daughter of {{ill|Yashimajin|ja|八島牟遅能神|1=Yashimamuji|1=Yashimamuji|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yashimajin|13=User:Immanuelle/Yashimamuji|qq=}}. Torinarumi-no-Kami married {{ill|Hinateri-Nukada-Bichio-Ikochini-no-Kami|ja|日名照額田毘道男伊許知邇神|1=Hinateri-Nukada-Bichio-Ikochini-no-Kami|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hinateri-Nukada-Bichio-Ikochini-no-Kami|13=User:Immanuelle/Hinateri-Nukada-Bichio-Ikochini-no-Kami|qq=}} and gave birth to {{ill|Kuninobutomi-no-Kami|ja|国忍富神|1=Kuninotoshimi-no-Kami|1=Kuninotoshimi-no-Kami|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kuninobutomi-no-Kami|13=User:Immanuelle/Kuninotoshimi-no-Kami|qq=}}.
== Shrines enshrining Torinarumi-no-Kami == * '''Narumi Shrine''' ({{ill|Inuyama|ja|犬山市|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Inuyama|qq=}}, {{ill|Aichi Prefecture|ja|愛知県|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Aichi Prefecture|qq=}}) - Main deity * '''Ueki Shrine''' ({{ill|Iga|ja|伊賀市|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Iga|qq=}}, {{ill|Mie Prefecture|ja|三重県|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mie Prefecture|qq=}}) - Enshrined alongside others * '''Tabika Shrine''' (Komono Town, {{ill|Mie District, Mie Prefecture|ja|三重郡|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mie District, Mie Prefecture|qq=}}) - Included in a [[Shrine Consolidation Policy|merger]]
*
