== Related articles == * {{ill|Kayanarumi no Kami|lt=Kayanarumi no Kami|lt=Kayanarumi|ja|カヤナルミ|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kayanarumi|qq=}} - A deity appearing in the ''{{ill|Engishiki|ja|延喜式|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Engishiki|qq=}}'' (巻八, ''Izumo Province Norito''), thought to have a connection due to the shared element "Narumi." * {{ill|Nunobutomi-Torinarumi-no-Kami|ja|布忍富鳥鳴海神|1=Nunobutomi-Torinarumi-no-Kami|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Nunobutomi-Torinarumi-no-Kami|13=User:Immanuelle/Nunobutomi-Torinarumi-no-Kami|qq=}} - The thirteenth generation deity among the Completion tier 3]] |ref={{SfnRef|Nishimiya|2014}} |author=[[Kazutami Nishimiya]] 校注 |isbn=978-4-10-620801-0 |series=[[Shinchō Nihon Koten Shūsei]] (new edition)}}
